  "texts": [
    "While 26.4% stayed neutral, 15.7% expressed disagreement, and 6.9% expressed strong disagreement.",
    "The mean is 3.44 which is considered high.",
    "The cumulative mean is 4.",
    "Of all the four elements, 72% of participants' parents possessed an attitude of positivity toward the English language learning.",
    "Similarly, the cumulative mean of students' and parents\" attitudes toward English language learning is 4."
  ]
